<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA71">
<l>kaḷiṟu mukilkuttak kaiyeṭut tōṭi</l>
<l>yoḷiṟu maruppocikai yāḷi – piḷiṟi</l>
<l>viḻakkoṉṟu niṉṟatirum vēṅkaṭamē mēṉāṭ</l>
<l>kuḻakkaṉṟu koṇṭeṟintāṉ kuṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Vēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l>where the bull elephant stands [and] trumpets after having, trunk raised</l>
<l>so that it pierces the clouds, run at [and] killed the Yāḷi , so that it fell,</l>
<l>roaring, [its] paw broken by the shining tusk,</l>
<l>is the hill of him who on a former day threw the young calf.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
